    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >《synopsis》</h2>After two worlds merged, conflicts that lasted for hundreds of years. Eventually, the flame of destruction slowly ignites in the crack.<br>Lead your legion on the epic journey to break the chains of hatred to save the world from the primordial darkness.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >《features》</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >■ Authentic turn-based strategic RPG based on the epic story.</h2>As you clear the stage of the world, you will play a role as the protagonist of the epic story.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >■ Deeper Strategy With Various Variables</h2>It is turn-based. Random weather changes, the day and night, terrain kind and combination between the hero and the soldier affect outcome of each battle. <br>Field of view at night will be limited. So, be careful.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164200/extras/015351aa68dbc3774fe4029bda3d89f2.poster.avif?t=1739970730\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164200/extras/015351aa68dbc3774fe4029bda3d89f2.webm?t=1739970730\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164200/extras/015351aa68dbc3774fe4029bda3d89f2.mp4?t=1739970730\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >■ Attractive Hero Characters</h2>Playable heroes will meet as you progress through the game and join when the time comes.<br>Use each hero's unique skills to win battles.<br>Not only most of the illustrations of heroes have their own animation, but also, attractive SD. And as you progress through the story, you can get exclusive equipment.<br>The dialogue varies depending on the level of favorability, so give gifts obtained at the ‘Summoning Station’ to increase likeability of each hero.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164200/extras/7d2e0569ba99fad92144a5f9ef6abc85.poster.avif?t=1739970730\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164200/extras/7d2e0569ba99fad92144a5f9ef6abc85.webm?t=1739970730\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164200/extras/7d2e0569ba99fad92144a5f9ef6abc85.mp4?t=1739970730\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164200/extras/ec6455694bbdb20eff7a11886047a91c.poster.avif?t=1739970730\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164200/extras/ec6455694bbdb20eff7a11886047a91c.webm?t=1739970730\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164200/extras/ec6455694bbdb20eff7a11886047a91c.mp4?t=1739970730\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >■ Job-changeable Soldiers</h2>Soldiers who have achieved the level requirement can change their job by consuming resources.<br>After changing job, soldier’s stats will be enhanced, and the appearance will be changed. (Appearance changes will be updated soon)<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >■ Easy Crafting and Smelting</h2>You can craft and smelt equipment by consuming materials. The success rate is 100%.<br>Sell equipment to get gold, disassemble it to get materials.<br>Equipment can be mounted on Heroes.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >■ the Airship!</h2>As the story progresses, you can board the Airship.<br>The airship function as a stronghold and, heroes move around on its deck.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164200/extras/7d3bee4968ac21d62ef243e190a359fd.poster.avif?t=1739970730\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164200/extras/7d3bee4968ac21d62ef243e190a359fd.webm?t=1739970730\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164200/extras/7d3bee4968ac21d62ef243e190a359fd.mp4?t=1739970730\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
